    public class CompoundedFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    This class is the frame which is used throughout the entire Compounded game. Time spent: 10 hours
    Version:
    1.0 May 16, 2014., 2.0 - May 23, 2014 - No changes made., 3.0 - May 30, 2014 - No changes made., 4.0 - June 6, 2014 - Added new method switchToMenu() which is used in the splashScreen() method to switch to the menu screen., 5.0 - No changes made.
    Author:
    Joshua Yuan
